body:
Varus wears a Gas mask, and fire suit, something similar to apocalyptic Brand

Passive will show flames on the Bow, when he kills a minion, and intense flames when he gets a kill or assist

Q should be a flaming arrow, maybe leave a flame trail.

W Should be flame stacks, or something ignitable with fire, on proc, should show flames comsuming the enemy for 1 sec or less

E should be a flaming destroyed ground, the arrows explode

R should throw flames at the enemy, while rooted they burn, and the fire spreads to the other champions.


He could say some quotes, like.

&quot;Ill show them agonny&quot;

&quot;Burn them, to show real agonny&quot;

&quot;I will be their death&quot;

&quot;Face me, i wanna see you burn&quot;

&quot;I will burn everything that comes in my way&quot;
